eZ SNMPd extension 0.1 installation instructions

- install eZ Publish


- install and activate the extension as per standard eZ Publish 4.0 procedures (regenerate autoloads)


- alter the snmpd.conf and restart the service. Example line to add:

pass_persist .1.3.6.1.4.1.35000.1 \var\www\eZ\extension\ezsnmpd\bin\php\ezSNMPagent.php

or

pass_persist .1.3.6.1.4.1.35000.1 \var\www\eZ\extension\ezsnmpd\bin\win\ezSNMPagent.bat


- test that the extension works by running

snmpget -v1 -c public -v 1 localhost 1.3.6.1.4.1.35000.1.2.1.1

(change the '-c public' param above to suit your snmp community string)


- you can retrieve the eZ Publish MIB to install in monitoring tools by pointing the browser at

http://my.ezpublish.site/index.php/siteaccess/snmp/mib

please note that by default that page is world-readable.